headline: Domino's Pizza Stock Gets RS Rating Lift
summary: One important metric to look for in a stock is an 80 or higher Relative Strength Rating.  Domino's Pizza stock just hit that mark, with a jump from 77 to 83 Thursday.  Over 100 years of market history shows that the best-performing stocks typically have an 80 or better RS Rating as they launch their biggest climbs.
